Sentencas: The idea of control strategy of SOFC operating to meet demand of a public utility building was presented.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: The strategy was formulated with the support of Artificial Neural Network.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: The network was used to predict the demand for electricity.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: The calculations were carried out on the example of a building of the Institute of Heat Engineering Warsaw University of Technology.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: The control strategy is influenced by various factors depending on changes in market conditions and operating characteristics of the cell.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: We can define different objective functions eg: working for own needs, for maximum profit and maximum service life.
Titulo: ANN-supported control strategy for a solid oxide fuel cell working on demand for a public utility building

Sentencas: The article presents a simulation of SOFC operation for demand profile of the IHE building from the selected time period.
